		<span id="title-175747259" class="story-title"> <a   href="//games.slashdot.org/story/24/12/24/1814214/2024-was-the-year-the-bottom-fell-out-of-the-games-industry">'2024 Was the Year the Bottom Fell Out of the Games Industry'</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.wired.com/story/2024-was-the-year-the-bottom-fell-out-of-the-games-industry/"  title="External link - https://www.wired.com/story/2024-was-the-year-the-bottom-fell-out-of-the-games-industry/" target="_blank"> (wired.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
